      • createSharedAlias

        public String createSharedAlias(String relationName)
        Description copied from interface: QLBuilder
        Create a shared alias for the specified relation name for use in QLBuilder.createJoin(JoinType, String, String).

        This is useful in cases where you want to use the same alias for multiple independent calls to QLBuilder.createJoin(JoinType, String, String), since joins are created per unique combination of relation name, join type, alias, and condition.

        Specified by:
        createSharedAlias in interface QLBuilder

        Returns:
        the alias.

      • uniqueParam

        public String uniqueParam(String parameterName,
                 Object parameterValue)
        Description copied from interface: QLBuilder
